# KlinikApp — Geliştirme Görevleri

## Sprint 0 — Altyapı ✅
- [x] NestJS backend scaffolding
- [x] Docker Compose (PostgreSQL + Redis)
- [x] Prisma schema + generate (14 model)
- [x] Environment config (.env)
- [x] Global filters, pipes, validation
- [x] Guards, Decorators, Interceptors
- [x] Auth module (JWT + refresh token)
- [x] Tüm 10 feature modül (controller + service)
- [x] Seed data + README
- [x] TypeScript derleme başarılı ✅

## Sprint 1 — Frontend & Auth ✅
- [x] Next.js 15 scaffolding (TypeScript, Tailwind, App Router)
- [x] Design system (globals.css — dark theme, CSS variables)
- [x] Axios API client (JWT auto-refresh)
- [x] Zustand auth store
- [x] Login sayfası
- [x] Sidebar layout (Adobe-style nav)
- [x] Dashboard (stat kartları, yaklaşan randevular, hızlı işlemler)
- [x] Placeholder sayfalar (takvim, mesajlar, hastalar, finans, notlar, ayarlar)
- [x] Root redirect (/ → /login)
- [x] Auth guard (unauthorized → login redirect) ✅

